  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of 5% Lidocaine Patch With Placebo Patch in Subjects With Herpes Zoster Associated Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Single and Multiple-Dose, Two-Period, Consecutive Study in Healthy Chinese Subjects to Assess the Pharmacokinetic Profiles, Safety and Tolerability of Lidocaine Patch 5%.LIG13-CN-101 Study</official_title>
