  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study designed to assess the efficacy
      and safety of 5% lidocaine patch, following placebo or active patch applications in placebo
      insensitive subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
